jmath.types

Class Matrix

  • java.lang.Object
    • jmath.types.MObject
      • jmath.types.IMatrix
        • jmath.types.Matrix

  • public class Matrix
extends IMatrix
    A class for performing matrix mathematics. in 3 dimensions. An object of this class represents a single 3-by-3 matrix
